      "comment": "CANYA CAVIAR (8) was in the placings last time but prior to that clocked a sharp 22.37 win over 400m at this track. Can measure up again if runs up to recent best times. NAUGHTY EVIE (1) overcame a collision in the run and scored in quick time latest (29.98) at Cannington over 520m in a Grade 5. This tougher but looks a leading chance again. DEAR ELIZA (2) hit the ground running last start and was never headed to land her maiden success over 488m at this track (27.78). Drawn well off an inside draw. Harder here but expected to measure up. MABEL MONELLI (6) continues to race well and is sure to be competitive again.",
